          <div class="contact-right-container col-md-10 p-5"> 
              <h5>Last updated: May 31, 2023</h5>
              <div class="col-md-12" style="margin: 0%">
                <p class="mx-2">At Testpod, we are committed to protecting your privacy and safeguarding your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect the data you provide when using our website and services.</p> 
                <h6>1. Information We Collect</h6>
                <div>
                    <p class="mx-2"><b>1.1</b> Personal Information: We may collect personal information, such as your name, email address, and demographic details, when you create an account or interact with our website. This information is used to personalize your experience, provide relevant content and updates, and enhance our services.</p>
