                <div>
                    <p class="mx-2">We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance your browsing experience, improve our website's functionality, and gather information about how you interact with our services. You can adjust your browser settings to manage or disable cookies, but please note that some features may not function properly without them.</p>
                </div>
                <h6>5. Third-Party Links</h6>
                <div>
                    <p class="mx-2">Our website may contain links to third-party websites, applications, or services. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of these third parties. We encourage you to review their privacy policies before providing any personal information.</p>
                </div>
                <h6>6. Children's Privacy</h6>
                <div>
