                </div>
                <h6>7. Updates to Privacy Policy</h6>
                <div>
                    <p class="mx-2">We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. We encourage you to review this policy periodically for any updates. Your continued use of our website and services after any modifications signifies your acceptance of the revised Privacy Policy.</p>
                </div>
